OL,3,CYoung people to lose benefits if they
OL,4,Crefuse work or training, minster says
OL,6,FYoung people will lose their benefits
OL,7,Fif they refuse to take up work and
OL,8,Ftraining opportunities, a Cabinet
OL,9,Fminister has said ahead of announcing
OL,10,Fmeasures to cut the welfare bill.
OL,12,FLiz Kendall said claimants have a
OL,13,F"responsibility" to engage with skills
OL,14,For employment programmes and will face
OL,15,Fsanctions if they decline to do so as
OL,16,Fpart of reforms to be set out next
OL,17,Fweek.
