OL,3,CYoung people to lose benefits if they
OL,4,Crefuse work or training, minster says
OL,6,FThe Labour government has said it will
OL,7,Fstick to a commitment under the former
OL,8,FTory administration to reduce the
OL,9,Fwelfare bill by #3 billion over five
OL,10,Fyears.
OL,12,FUnder the previous government, welfare
OL,13,Feligibility would have been tightened
OL,14,Fso around 400,000 more people signed
OL,15,Foff long-term would be assessed as
OL,16,Fneeding to prepare for work by 2028/29
OL,17,Fto deliver the savings.
