OL,4,Crefuse work or training, minster says
OL,6,FFacing broadcasters on Sunday, Ms
OL,7,FKendall declined to reveal how
OL,8,Fspecifically Labour will cut costs
OL,9,Fahead of announcing a package of
OL,10,Flegislation next week, saying only the
OL,11,Fgovernment will introduce its own
OL,12,Freforms.
OL,14,FThe Work and Pensions Secretary told
OL,15,FSunday Morning With Trevor Phillips on
OL,16,FSky News: "If people repeatedly refuse
OL,17,Fto take up the training or work
OL,18,Fresponsibilities, there will be
OL,19,Fsanctions on their benefits.
