OL,3,CYoung people to lose benefits if they
OL,4,Crefuse work or training, minster says
OL,6,F"The reason why we believe this so
OL,7,Fstrongly is that we believe in our
OL,8,Fresponsibility to provide those
OL,9,Fopportunities, which is what we will
OL,10,Fdo."
OL,12,FReferring to young people
OL,13,Fspecifically, she said the government
OL,14,Fwould "transform" opportunities with a
OL,15,F"youth guarantee" as part of the
OL,16,Freforms, but they would in turn be
OL,17,F"required to take them up".
