OL,3,CYoung people to lose benefits if they
OL,4,Crefuse work or training, minster says
OL,6,FMs Kendall also said she believed
OL,7,F"many millions" of disabled people and
OL,8,Fthose with long-term health problems
OL,9,Fwant to work, and "we need to break
OL,10,Fdown the barriers to that happening".
OL,12,FThe latest official forecasts
OL,13,Fpublished by the government show the
OL,14,Fnumber of people claiming incapacity
OL,15,Fbenefits is expected to climb from
OL,16,Faround 2.5 million in 2019 to 4.2
OL,17,Fmillion in 2029. Last year there were
OL,18,Fjust over three million claimants.
