OL,3,CYoung people to lose benefits if they
OL,4,Crefuse work or training, minster says
OL,6,FMs Kendall will set out a package of
OL,7,Fmeasures on Tuesday designed to "get
OL,8,FBritain working" amid Government
OL,9,Fconcerns about the projected rise.
OL,11,FHer white paper is expected to include
OL,12,Fthe placement of work coaches in
OL,13,Fmental health clinics and a "youth
OL,14,Fguarantee" aimed at ensuring those
OL,15,Faged 18-21 are working or studying.
OL,17,FThe Cabinet minister said the reasons
OL,18,Ffor the increased number of claims are
OL,19,F"complex" and that Britain is "an
OL,20,Folder and also sicker nation".
